    "body": "Hi @vvo ?\r\n\r\nI guess I'm experiencing an issue with this, take a look at the screenshots please:\r\n\r\n![Screenshot 2023-03-02 at 13 34 48](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16926778/222430940-56963475-79d1-41f9-bb10-bfe63618a675.png)\r\n![Screenshot 2023-03-02 at 13 34 57](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16926778/222430941-49aedd2d-24f5-4803-827f-87a3413560c6.png)\r\n![Screenshot 2023-03-02 at 13 34 23](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16926778/222430932-c567973a-b565-4023-be51-497eb88d88da.png)\r\n\r\nAs you can see I have the list of country_iso as my facet values, and there are around 200 countries, so I set this limit, but all I can see both in the dashboard plus on the UI side (with Vue InstantSearch lib) is 100 values. \r\n\r\nDid I miss something? ",
